	{
		name: 'Events',
		description:
			'Lyft vegan before they sold out prism pickled, cloud bread la croix fit. Gastropub schlitz blog art party scenester pour-over. Marfa shabby chic lo-fi coloring book gochujang air plant, yuccie echo park skateboard wolf typewriter poutine.',
	},
	{
		name: 'Catering',
		description:
			'Street art palo santo yes plz 8-bit, la croix tumblr mukbang bruh. Shabby chic tousled letterpress meditation, photo booth 3 wolf moon artisan yr locavore flannel cloud bread trust fund. Brunch lumbersexual semiotics big mood portland celiac.',
	},
	{
